seal     : Once the text is tokens, each token is replaced by a vector — a long list of numbers — and those numbers are coordinates. Every token becomes a point in a high-dimensional space of meaning, where words used in similar ways sit near each other. The text stops being a stream and becomes a place. Meaning, made geometry.
